ActBank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Finance of JEAN-GUY DESJARDINS of Westmount, Quebec, and PAUL D. DICKS, Q.C., of St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador, as directors of the Board of Directors of the Bank of Canada to hold office, during good behaviour, for a term beginning on March 1, 2005 and ending on February 29, 2008.
